	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The powerpak is good for FDS games as it's fast at swapping "disks" automatically, and the loading times present on all emulators somehow are skipped.
<br />
<br />However, for all other games it's pretty much the same as playing under an accurate emulator with NTSC filter turned on.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


